        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Verdana" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700">
            Boston Pension Fund Seeks Hedge Fund Managers
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="EB Garamond" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6">
            The $7bn pension fund is accepting proposals exclusively from
            managers of multi-strategy hedge funds of funds.
            <a
              href="https://www.pionline.com/influential-women-institutional-investing/nepcs-krissy-pelletier-named-pis-2024-class-influential"
              target="_blank"
              >NEPC is managing</a
            >
            the search process. The RFP states that the pension fund may add new
            managers or retain its current managers, Blackstone and GCM
            Grosvenor. As of 30 June, the two firms managed $166m and $176m. As
            of the same date, the actual allocation to hedge funds was 4.9% of
            the pension fund’s assets, slightly below its 5% target.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider
          border-width="1px"
          border-style="solid"
          border-color="lightgrey"
          padding-top="20px"
        />
